³  TV RULES:                                                                 ³
³                                                                            ³
³ - 1 Card = 458mb                                                           ³
³ - Episodes shall not overlap on Cards (i.e. 2eps/Card, 4eps/Card           ³
³   is allowed, 1.5eps/Card is NOT).                                         ³
³ - Episodes are not subject to the same scaling rules as cinematic          ³
³   features and must obey forementioned rule.                               ³
