³        Source release                                                      ³
³        Audio bitrate                                                       ³
³        Framesize/aspect ratio                                              ³
³        Video bitrate                                                       ³
³        Source used (Xvid/DVDR) and (TC/TS/DVD/DVDSCR/HDTV/PDTV)            ³
